</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/50015675-polly-mclean"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1449867386i/50015675._UX100_CR0,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/50015675-polly-mclean">Polly McLean</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I thought that it was more to highlight the difference time has made to the way women&apos;s behaviour is judged. Iris&apos;s nonconformity to social norms isn&apos;<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I thought that it was more to highlight the difference time has made to the way women's behaviour is judged. Iris's nonconformity to social norms isn't considered especially odd and doesn't have any negative impact on her her life or well-being, while Esme's lesser nonconformity causes her to be deprived of her freedom for 61 years. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
