<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/56856599-the-disappearance-of-esme-lennox"><img alt="The disappearance of Esme Lennox" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/book/111x148-bcc042a9c91a29c1d680899eff700a03.png" />
